Package: webtty
Version: ${VERSION}
Section: web
Priority: optional
Architecture: amd64
Depends: libc6 (>= 2.36)
Maintainer: WebTTY Maintainers
Homepage: https://github.com/anthropics/webtty
Description: Self-hosted web terminal
 A self-hosted web terminal that brings the full power of your server
 to any browser. Supports bash, zsh, fish, nushell with oh-my-zsh
 themes, file browser, multi-tab interface, and Catppuccin UI.
 .
 Installed as a systemd service with security hardening.
